did Than trick you into coming here?

33
00:02:34,970 --> 00:02:36,790
- I've never tricked anyone in my life.
- Mm.

34
00:02:37,170 --> 00:02:38,040
Excuse me, Mr. Phana.

35
00:02:39,010 --> 00:02:40,490
Oh! You're burning up.

36
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,280
Let me stay with you tonight.

37
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,660
If I want you to sleep with me tonight,

38
00:02:46,110 --> 00:02:46,980
how much would you charge?

39
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:49,530
I don't think you'd be foolish enough

40
00:02:49,970 --> 00:02:51,770
to refuse my offer.

41
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,880
You're the foolish one.

42
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:57,060
When I want something, I get it.

43
00:02:59,460 --> 00:02:59,920
Hey!

44
00:03:00,770 --> 00:03:01,720
Who the hell?

45
00:03:01,850 --> 00:03:02,830
I told you, didn't I?

46
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,330
Stay the hell away from Nawa.

47
00:03:06,610 --> 00:03:08,300
I know I've already asked before.

48
00:03:08,650 --> 00:03:10,020
But let me ask again.

49
00:03:10,890 --> 00:03:13,400
Please let me take care of you, always.

50
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:15,550
You don't have to be perfect.

51
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,130
Just be yourself.

52
00:03:18,950 --> 00:03:20,290
That's all it takes for me to love you.

53
00:03:33,230 --> 00:03:34,300
Will you be my boyfriend?

54
